<h2 class="wikipedia">Wikipedia</h2>
<div class="wikipedia-extract-body wikipedia-extract-collapse"><p><b>Giovanni Bottesini</b> (22 December 1821 – 7 July 1889), was an Italian Romantic composer, conductor, and a double bass virtuoso.</p>
<p></p></div>
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Giovanni_Bottesini">Continue reading at Wikipedia...</a>
